## 4.3 Key-Value Pair Transformation Matrix

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    P1[Input Record\nK1: Byte Offset 0\nV1: Hadoop is great] --> P2[Tokenizer Splits\nhadoop, is, great]
    P2 --> P3{Is token in\nKEYWORDS HashSet}
    P3 -->|Yes hadoop| P4[Emit K2: hadoop\nV2: 1]
    P3 -->|No is| P5[Skip and Discard]
    P3 -->|No great| P5
    P4 --> P6[Intermediate Output\nAll Mappers Emit to Framework]
    P6 --> P7[Shuffle and Sort\nGroup by Key]
    P7 --> P8[Reducer Input\nhadoop: list of 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
    P8 --> P9[Sum Aggregation\nhadoop: 5]
    P9 --> P10[Final Output\nK3: hadoop\nV3: 5]
```

