**Q (a)** Write the complete Java code for a Hadoop MapReduce program that reads a text file from HDFS and computes the **average length of words starting with each alphabet character** (A–Z, case-insensitive). Include the Mapper, Reducer, and Driver classes with appropriate type parameters.

**Q (b)** Explain the role of the `Partitioner` and `Combiner` in this program. What would happen if we set `job.setNumReduceTasks(0)`? Justify your answer with a real-world example.

